org.sql: SELECT changesets.* FROM changesets WHERE changesets.repository_id = "$1" AND scmid IN ('713f4944648826f558cf548222f813dabe7cbb04', '61b685fbe55ab05b5ac68402d5720c1a6ac973d1') ORDER BY changesets.committed_on DESC, changesets.id DESC, committed_on DESC
